# Migration + schema sync

Editing `migrations/*.sql` or a `*.schema.ts`? Run **[db-migration-maintainer](../skills/db-migration-maintainer/SKILL.md)** (and **[sql-design-guard](../skills/sql-design-guard/SKILL.md)** for schemas). Gate: `pnpm db:migrate:lint`. Applied migrations are immutable — add a new one. Full chain: `schema-change` in `agent-os/skills/chains.json`.
